Title : Neon Light Button Animation Effects on Hover || HTML & CSS

Description : Neon animation is one of the most important part of css programming language. 
HTML code is used to create the structure of such animations and css programming code is used to design. 
Neon light animation is used on various topics such as buttons, text, lines, boxes, etc. In this case hover effect is added. 
When the mouse is moved over that text or button, the neon color will appear brighter.

Source Code : https://github.com/Bhuvanagsp2/Neon_AnimationButton.git

